Model Evaluation Tab
The Model Evaluation tab provides information about a model’s performance and cross-validation results.

In Performance, click Model Evaluation.
For model evaluation details, click a subtab.
Overall Performance Tab
The Overall Performance tab shows key metrics for model quality.
Cross Validation Tab
To test a model’s ability to make predictions, Einstein Discovery uses k-fold cross-validation. This tab summarizes the results of the cross-validation process.
